    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no chips, scratches, or dings. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a new vehicle.",
