      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic companion and is still in great shape for its next owner! It runs super smoothly and has been really well-cared for over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks sharp on the road. I've loved driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in high-revving atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band that screams to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity, and the VANOS system has been recently serviced for timing precision. The suspension maintains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings, offering the telepathic steering feedback this platform is renowned for. While showing minor signs of use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul\u2014are robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliable performance. The exterior is finished in a deep sapphire metallic that retains a brilliant luster, having been garage-kept and frequently detailed; while the front fascia shows a few minor, honest rock chips from highway driving, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Step inside to a smoke-free cabin where the premium charcoal leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, power sunroof, and high-fidelity sound system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health with a documented service history. It recently underwent a full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires offer approximately 70% tread life, and the braking system feels firm and responsive. On the road, the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a quiet, refined ride that feels as solid today as it did when new. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term reliability. This example exhibits a clean aesthetic and has been serviced to ensure a seamless driving experience. An excellent opportunity for the professional seeking a sophisticated and dependable transport solution at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and she\u2019s still in really wonderful shape! She\u2019s been super reliable for me and is ready to hit the road with a new owner who will appreciate her just as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable ride that still feels great and looks sharp, this is the one for you. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take her for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is crisp, and the Vanos system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue. While showing honest patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver, the compression numbers are strong across all cylinders, and the throttle response remains razor-sharp.",
